WEBVTT

01:46.083 --> 01:48.208
PREVIOUSLY ON "DEXTER"...

01:48.208 --> 01:49.834
THINK THIS IS
OUR GUY'S WORK?

01:49.834 --> 01:51.500
THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER?

01:51.500 --> 01:53.083
LaGUERTA INSULTED THE REAL
KILLER'S INTELLIGENCE,

01:53.083 --> 01:54.542
AND NOW HE'S
GETTING BACK AT US

01:54.542 --> 01:56.250
FOR CHASING AFTER
THE WRONG GUY.

01:56.250 --> 01:59.041
IT'S THE GUARD -- TUCCI.
I THINK HE'S ALIVE.

01:59.041 --> 02:00.917
TUCCI'S ALIVE?

02:00.917 --> 02:03.375
THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER
IS KEEPING HIM ALIVE

02:03.375 --> 02:04.834
TO PERFORM AMPUTATIONS.

02:04.834 --> 02:06.917
Dexter:
HE'S SENDING ME A MESSAGE.

02:06.917 --> 02:08.750
HE WANTS ME TO GO THERE.

02:10.625 --> 02:12.166
PLEASE.

02:12.166 --> 02:13.750
HE WAS LEFT HERE
SO I WOULD KILL HIM.

02:13.750 --> 02:14.750
JUST KILL ME.

02:14.750 --> 02:17.333
I CAN'T KILL THIS MAN.

02:18.583 --> 02:21.083
Matthews: I'M TAKING TUCCI
OVER TO COUNTY ALIVE.

02:21.083 --> 02:23.208
I DON'T KNOW WHO
YOUR CONTACTS ARE, MORGAN,

02:23.208 --> 02:25.041
BUT YOU ARE
MY UP-AND-COMER.

02:25.041 --> 02:27.041
YOU SAVED
A MAN'S LIFE TONIGHT.

02:27.041 --> 02:29.083
THE THING THAT SURPRISES ME
MOST ABOUT RITA

02:29.083 --> 02:32.000
IS HOW MUCH I LIKE
BEING WITH HER.

02:32.000 --> 02:35.583
THERE'S ALL SORTS OF THINGS
I CAN DO.

02:41.917 --> 02:43.417
[ ZIPPER UNZIPS ]

02:43.417 --> 02:45.583
WHAT -- WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

02:45.583 --> 02:47.583
WHATEVER I WANT.

02:47.583 --> 02:49.542
[ CHUCKLES ]

02:49.542 --> 02:51.959
MY NEW FRIEND THOUGHT
I WOULDN'T BE ABLE TO RESIST

02:51.959 --> 02:53.667
THE KILL HE LEFT FOR ME,

02:53.667 --> 02:56.291
BUT I DID.

02:56.291 --> 02:59.709
I'M NOT THE MONSTER
HE WANTS ME TO BE.

02:59.709 --> 03:02.375
I'M DEXTER.

03:13.375 --> 03:17.875
I LIKE TO PRETEND I'M ALONE,
COMPLETELY ALONE,

03:17.875 --> 03:22.792
MAYBE POST-APOCALYPSE
OR PLAGUE,

03:22.792 --> 03:24.125
WHATEVER --

03:24.125 --> 03:26.291
NO ONE LEFT TO ACT NORMAL FOR,

03:26.291 --> 03:30.083
NO NEED TO HIDE
WHO I REALLY AM.

03:30.083 --> 03:33.792
IT WOULD BE FREEING.

03:33.792 --> 03:36.041
Doakes: STOP GRINNING
LIKE A FUCKING PSYCHO

03:36.041 --> 03:37.667
AND GET BACK TO WORK.

03:37.667 --> 03:39.000
SORRY, SERGEANT.

03:39.000 --> 03:41.041
I WAS JUST WAITING
FOR FORENSICS TO WRAP UP

03:41.041 --> 03:44.208
BEFORE I TEAR
THE BED APART.

03:44.208 --> 03:48.041
I'M NOT THE ONLY ONE
WHO ENJOYS ISOLATION.

03:50.208 --> 03:53.208
MY SHADOW COMPANION
CHOSE THIS PLACE WELL.

03:58.667 --> 04:01.000
THIS WAS HIS SANCTUARY,

04:01.000 --> 04:03.166
FOR A WHILE, AT LEAST.

04:03.166 --> 04:07.375
ALL THESE PEOPLE
PAWING OVER IT SEEMS...

04:07.375 --> 04:10.041
DISRESPECTFUL.

04:10.041 --> 04:12.625
[ LaGUERTA SPEAKING
INDISTINCTLY ]

04:12.625 --> 04:15.500
TELL ME THE SICK BASTARD
BLED ON SOMETHING, DEXTER.

04:15.500 --> 04:17.583
HE WAS HERE FOR DAYS,
PLAYING WITH SHARP OBJECTS.

04:17.583 --> 04:19.959
I'LL KEEP LOOKING, BUT SO FAR
THIS PLACE IS SPOTLESS,

04:19.959 --> 04:21.542
AMAZINGLY SO.

04:21.542 --> 04:24.041
THE ONLY BLOOD I FOUND BELONGS
TO THE SECURITY GUARD.

04:24.041 --> 04:25.291
HAS HE SAID ANYTHING YET?

04:25.291 --> 04:26.959
MR. TUCCI'S
STILL UNCONSCIOUS.

04:26.959 --> 04:28.625
Man: LIEUTENANT, UP HERE!

04:28.625 --> 04:30.542
THERE'S GOT TO BE
SOMETHING HERE. FIND IT.

04:30.542 --> 04:33.709
THE GUY'S NOT A GHOST.
TONY TUCCI IS EVIDENCE OF THAT.

04:35.291 --> 04:37.917
HEY, DEXTER, YOU GET
ALL THIS BLOOD ON CAMERA YET?

04:37.917 --> 04:40.083
IT'S LIKE SHOOTING
A JACKSON POLLOCK.

04:40.083 --> 04:41.709
[ CHUCKLES ]

04:45.959 --> 04:49.709
WELL, YOUR JACKSON POLLOCK
IS IN THE BAG.

04:52.083 --> 04:53.750
READY?

04:53.750 --> 04:55.291
OKAY.

04:57.583 --> 05:00.041
WHOA. WHAT WAS THAT?
DID YOU SEE THAT?

05:00.041 --> 05:01.417
WHAT?

05:01.417 --> 05:02.667
DAMN RATS.

05:02.667 --> 05:05.208
WE'RE ALL GONNA
GET HISTOPLASMOSIS

05:05.208 --> 05:07.417
FROM ALL THEIR SHIT
IN THE DUST.

05:07.417 --> 05:11.917
WE'LL BE COUGHING UP BLOOD,
SKIN LESIONS, MOUTH SORES.

05:11.917 --> 05:14.291
LOVELY.
CAN WE GET THE LIGHTS, GUYS?

05:17.083 --> 05:19.917
YOU EVER HEARD
OF RAT-BITE FEVER?

05:19.917 --> 05:23.417
MASUKA, WHAT'D I SAY
ABOUT THE FUCKING RATS?

05:34.750 --> 05:37.500
YOU HAVEN'T FOUND ANYTHING,
WON'T FIND ANYTHING.

05:37.500 --> 05:38.959
THIS IS A BUST, RIGHT?

05:38.959 --> 05:40.959
IN SO MANY WORDS.

05:40.959 --> 05:43.917
WHICH MEANS I'M JUST JERKING OFF
TILL TUCCI WAKES UP.

05:43.917 --> 05:45.208
SO TAKE A BREAK.

05:45.208 --> 05:47.291
YOU'VE BEEN WORKING
THIS THING 24-7.

05:47.291 --> 05:49.625
OR ARE YOU STILL AVOIDING
A PERSONAL LIFE?

05:49.625 --> 05:51.250
OH, FUCK YOU.

05:51.250 --> 05:53.583
AND, YEAH, I'M BETTER OFF
JUST FOCUSING ON THE JOB.

05:53.583 --> 05:56.583
THANKS, GUYS.

05:56.583 --> 05:58.792
IT DOESN'T HAVE TO BE
EITHER/OR.

05:58.792 --> 06:00.709
MAYBE NOT FOR YOU.

06:00.709 --> 06:02.792
IF I FOUND SOMEONE,
SO CAN YOU, RIGHT?

06:02.792 --> 06:05.667
YEAH, THE TROUBLE IS
KEEPING THEM.

06:05.667 --> 06:08.709
TELL ME ABOUT IT.

06:30.041 --> 06:31.959
YELINA?

06:31.959 --> 06:33.583
ARE YOU OKAY?

06:33.583 --> 06:36.333
I'M SORRY. I'M FINE.

06:36.333 --> 06:37.542
[ SNIFFLES ]

06:37.542 --> 06:39.667
ERNESTO HASN'T ARRIVED?

06:45.291 --> 06:47.000
[ SNIFFLING ]

06:49.250 --> 06:51.750
I'M SURE
HE'LL BE HERE SOON.

06:51.750 --> 06:53.625
NO.

06:53.625 --> 06:56.250
THE COYOTE WANTED MORE MONEY,
AND I DIDN'T HAVE IT.

06:57.834 --> 06:59.542
COYOTE?

06:59.542 --> 07:02.375
YOU MEAN THE MAN YOU PAID
TO BRING HIM HERE?

07:02.375 --> 07:05.417
HE SAID HE SENT ERNESTO
BACK TO CUBA.

07:05.417 --> 07:07.333
BUT THAT WAS A WEEK AGO,

07:07.333 --> 07:09.750
AND NO ONE IN CáRDENAS
HAS HEARD FROM ERNESTO.

07:09.750 --> 07:13.667
YELINA, HOW DID YOU CONTACT
THIS COYOTE?

07:13.667 --> 07:15.542
UM...

07:18.041 --> 07:21.875
...THIS WAS HIS NUMBER,
BUT IT'S NOT WORKING ANYMORE.

07:21.875 --> 07:24.542
I WAS SUPPOSED TO LEAVE HIM
MONEY IN A PARK.

07:24.542 --> 07:26.792
LISTEN, MY BOYFRIEND
WORKS FOR THE POLICE.

07:26.792 --> 07:28.083
I'M SURE HE --

07:28.083 --> 07:30.375
NO, NO, NO.
WE CAN'T GO TO THE POLICE.

07:30.375 --> 07:32.959
HE SAID HE'D HURT MY FAMILY
IN CUBA IF WE GO TO THE POLICE.

07:32.959 --> 07:35.041
NO, IT'S OKAY.
IT'S OKAY.

07:35.041 --> 07:36.792
DEXTER WILL KNOW
WHAT TO DO.

07:44.250 --> 07:46.709
I FEEL JUST TERRIBLE
FOR HER.

07:46.709 --> 07:49.542
AND THEY WERE SUPPOSED TO BE
MARRIED AFTER HE GOT HERE.

07:49.542 --> 07:52.417
I DO KNOW SOMEONE
IN THE DEPARTMENT

07:52.417 --> 07:54.083
WHO DEALS
WITH IMMIGRATION ISSUES.

07:54.083 --> 07:55.709
I CAN TALK TO HIM.

07:55.709 --> 07:57.542
THAT'S REALLY
KIND OF YOU, DEX.

07:57.542 --> 07:59.250
I MEAN, CAN YOU IMAGINE

07:59.250 --> 08:03.250
NOT KNOWING IF YOUR FIANCéE
IS DEAD OR ALIVE?

08:03.250 --> 08:05.458
UH, NO.

08:05.458 --> 08:07.667
EVERY NIGHT AFTER WORK
YELINA GOES ACROSS THE STREET,

08:07.667 --> 08:09.083
TO THE BEACH.

08:09.083 --> 08:11.333
I'VE SEEN HER THERE,

08:11.333 --> 08:13.750
JUST STARING OUT
AT THE WATER,

08:13.750 --> 08:16.417
WILLING HIM
TO WALK OUT OF IT.

08:18.583 --> 08:22.709
HAVE YOU EVER LONGED
FOR ANYTHING LIKE THAT?

08:25.125 --> 08:26.792
SHE WANTS SOMETHING FROM ME.

08:26.792 --> 08:28.583
EVER SINCE THE BLOW JOB,

08:28.583 --> 08:30.792
SHE ASSUMES WE'VE TAKEN IT
TO THE NEXT LEVEL.

08:30.792 --> 08:34.166
SHE DOESN'T KNOW YET --
I DON'T HAVE A NEXT LEVEL.

08:34.166 --> 08:35.625
WELL, WHEN I WAS A KID,

08:35.625 --> 08:38.083
I WOULD HAVE KILLED
FOR AN ATARI.

08:38.083 --> 08:39.792
YOU KNOW?

08:39.792 --> 08:44.333
CODY WOULD LAUGH AT THE GRAPHICS
NOW, BUT BACK THEN, MAN...

08:46.959 --> 08:48.458
MMM.

08:48.458 --> 08:50.417
IT ALWAYS COMES TO THIS
ONCE SEX IS INTRODUCED.

08:50.417 --> 08:52.375
SMALL TALK NO LONGER CUTS IT.

08:52.375 --> 08:54.542
EVENTUALLY SHE'LL CALL ME
A SCIENCE PROJECT

08:54.542 --> 08:57.291
AND SLAM THE DOOR IN MY FACE.

08:57.291 --> 09:00.709
BUT WHEN DO YOU THINK
HE'LL WAKE UP?

09:00.709 --> 09:03.000
YEAH, I DID CALL
AN HOUR AGO,

09:03.000 --> 09:04.500
BUT THERE'S A KILLER
OUT THERE

09:04.500 --> 09:06.500
THAT'S INTO WHORES
AND SECURITY GUARDS,

09:06.500 --> 09:09.083
BUT I'LL BET NURSES
ARE NEXT.

09:09.083 --> 09:12.667
YO, CHECK YOU,
ALL "MPD BLUE."

09:12.667 --> 09:14.625
SHANDA,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

09:14.625 --> 09:16.709
YOU HAVE ANOTHER LEAD
ON THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER?

09:16.709 --> 09:19.291
MAN, I GOT BIGGER WORRIES
THAN THAT SICK SHIT.

09:19.291 --> 09:21.792
NOW, I GOT ME A GIRL
ON THE INSIDE, RIGHT?

09:21.792 --> 09:24.125
I'M NOT SPRINGING YOUR PIMP,
IF THAT'S WHAT YOU'RE AFTER.

09:24.125 --> 09:25.583
OH, HELL, NO.

09:25.583 --> 09:27.375
BUT MY LANDLORD'S
ANOTHER FUCKING STORY --

09:27.375 --> 09:29.208
TRYING TO KICK ME
OUT OF MY HOME.

09:29.208 --> 09:30.709
HE GOT NO CAUSE,

09:30.709 --> 09:33.291
EXCEPT HE'S A BORN-AGAIN
HYPOCRITE MOTHERFUCKER.

09:33.291 --> 09:35.291
YEAH, AND YOU WANT ME
TO TALK TO HIM?

09:35.291 --> 09:37.125
NO, I WANT YOU TO BEAT IN
HIS PASTY, WHITE FACE.

09:37.125 --> 09:39.750
Doakes: MORGAN.

09:39.750 --> 09:41.875
FOUND THIS IN EVIDENCE.

09:41.875 --> 09:44.458
MASUKA WAS GONNA
GREASE IT THROUGH.

09:44.458 --> 09:46.041
A CIGARETTE BUTT?

09:46.041 --> 09:48.458
JESUS, WE COULD PULL DNA
OFF OF THAT, OR EVEN A PRINT.

09:48.458 --> 09:50.291
EXCEPT IT WOULD BE
YOUR  PRINT.

09:50.291 --> 09:52.542
YOU WERE SMOKING
ON A CRIME SCENE.

09:52.542 --> 09:54.709
NOT ON  THE CRIME SCENE --

09:54.709 --> 09:56.709
LIKE ON THE WAY-FAR END
OF THE PARK.

09:56.709 --> 09:58.709
THE WHOLE AREA'S
A CRIME SCENE.

09:58.709 --> 10:00.458
YOU SHOULD KNOW THAT BY NOW.

10:00.458 --> 10:02.500
MAYBE YOU OUGHT TO JUST CALM
THE HELL DOWN, MY BROTHER.

10:02.500 --> 10:03.875
WHO THE FUCK IS THAT?

10:03.875 --> 10:07.375
GIVE IT A REST, SHANDA.

10:07.375 --> 10:09.542
MORGAN,
GO DO SOMETHING USEFUL.

10:09.542 --> 10:12.417
GO SIT ON THAT SECURITY GUARD
UNTIL HE WAKES UP.

10:12.417 --> 10:14.917
AND DO NOT TALK TO HIM
WITHOUT ME.

10:16.834 --> 10:18.250
BELIEVE ME --

10:18.250 --> 10:20.375
YOUR MAID IS NOT THE FIRST ONE
TO GET SCREWED.

10:20.375 --> 10:24.041
NO, SHE'S A  MAID.
SHE'S NOT MY  MAID.

10:24.041 --> 10:25.667
SO, HAVE YOU HEARD

10:25.667 --> 10:28.291
OF ANY OTHER CUBAN IMMIGRANTS
DISAPPEARING?

10:28.291 --> 10:30.500
A FEW.
THE POOR BASTARDS.

10:30.500 --> 10:32.250
THEY SPEND
THEIR LIFE SAVINGS,

10:32.250 --> 10:33.792
GET STUFFED INTO A FISHHOLD,

10:33.792 --> 10:36.083
PUKE THE WHOLE
90 MILES TO MIAMI.

10:36.083 --> 10:38.792
THEN THEY GET HERE, THINKING,
"I'M AN AMERICAN. I'M FREE."

10:38.792 --> 10:42.583
EXCEPT THE DAMN COYOTE...

10:42.583 --> 10:44.333
HE WON'T LET THEM GO

10:44.333 --> 10:48.083
TILL HIS FAMILY COMES UP
WITH A SURPRISE RELEASE FEE.

10:50.250 --> 10:52.250
IF THEY CAN'T PAY...

10:52.250 --> 10:54.083
THEY DISAPPEAR.

10:54.083 --> 10:57.458
FREEDOM'S JUST ANOTHER WORD
FOR ONE MORE WAY TO GET FUCKED.

11:00.250 --> 11:03.417
SOUNDS LIKE SOMEONE'S
DOING SOMETHING VERY BAD.

11:06.250 --> 11:08.250
YOU HAVE ANY SUSPECTS?

11:08.250 --> 11:10.291
SURE, FOUR OR FIVE,

11:10.291 --> 11:11.792
MOSTLY CUBANS THEMSELVES,

11:11.792 --> 11:14.375
BUT NOT ENOUGH EVIDENCE
FOR A CONVICTION

11:14.375 --> 11:16.250
OR EVEN A WARRANT.

11:16.250 --> 11:17.792
IF WARRANTS WERE APPLIED FOR,

11:17.792 --> 11:19.792
THEIR NAMES WILL BE
IN THE DATABASE.

11:22.291 --> 11:23.583
LOOK, BUDDY...

11:23.583 --> 11:25.834
I KNOW YOU WANT
TO HELP OUT YOUR MAID,

11:25.834 --> 11:28.792
BUT THERE AIN'T A HELL OF A LOT
YOU CAN DO.

11:31.291 --> 11:33.542
YOU'D BE SURPRISED.

11:52.709 --> 11:54.792
JORGE CASTILLO --

11:54.792 --> 11:57.458
NUMBER 3 ON THE DEPARTMENT'S
LIST OF SUSPECTS,

11:57.458 --> 12:00.792
BUT THE ONLY ONE EVEN
REMOTELY CLOSE TO THE PARK

12:00.792 --> 12:03.250
WHERE YELINA WAS SUPPOSED
TO DROP THE MONEY.

12:05.250 --> 12:08.250
THEY NEVER GOT ENOUGH EVIDENCE
FOR A SEARCH WARRANT,

12:08.250 --> 12:11.834
BUT I DON'T NEED PERMISSION
TO KEEP AN EYE ON THIS GUY.

12:27.583 --> 12:30.000
NO NEIGHBORS,
NO FOOT TRAFFIC --

12:30.000 --> 12:31.917
IT'S PROMISING.

12:34.500 --> 12:36.875
A GOOD PLACE
FOR HUMAN TRAFFICKING...

12:36.875 --> 12:38.959
OR WORSE.

12:44.583 --> 12:46.375
EXCUSE ME.

12:46.375 --> 12:48.125
PRIVATE YARD.

12:48.125 --> 12:51.458
I'M JUST PRAYING YOU HAVE
A '69 STINGRAY HEADLIGHT

12:51.458 --> 12:53.417
SOMEWHERE IN HERE.

12:53.417 --> 12:55.250
UH, DAVE CUTLER.

12:55.250 --> 12:57.333
JORGE CASTILLO.

12:57.333 --> 12:58.750
I'M SORRY, BUT I DON'T.

12:58.750 --> 13:00.875
MAN, MY RESTORATION'S
ALMOST DONE.

13:00.875 --> 13:02.417
SHE'S A BEAUTY.

13:02.417 --> 13:04.583
I DON'T DO INDIVIDUAL SALES,
MR. CUTLER,

13:04.583 --> 13:07.000
BUT I CAN GIVE YOU THE NAME
OF A CORVETTE SHOP I DEAL WITH.

13:07.000 --> 13:10.125
I'LL BE HAPPY
TO LOOK AROUND MYSELF.

13:10.125 --> 13:13.750
NO OFFENSE, MAN,
BUT I CAN'T TAKE MY PHONE ORDERS

13:13.750 --> 13:15.750
IF I'M WATCHING OVER
MY MERCHANDISE.

13:15.750 --> 13:18.250
YOU RUN
THIS WHOLE PLACE ALONE?

13:18.250 --> 13:19.917
YEAH, IT KEEPS MY COSTS DOWN.

13:19.917 --> 13:22.750
HEY, I'M SORRY
YOU MADE THE TRIP OUT HERE.

13:22.750 --> 13:25.709
YOU KNOW WHAT?

13:25.709 --> 13:27.917
TRY WEXLER'S,
OUT IN TAMARAC.

13:27.917 --> 13:29.417
THAT'S MY VETTE GUY.

13:29.417 --> 13:31.166
YEAH.

13:31.166 --> 13:33.041
MUST BE NICE
BEING YOUR OWN BOSS --

13:33.041 --> 13:35.041
GET OUT IN THE WATER
WHENEVER YOU WANT.

13:35.041 --> 13:36.875
I SAW THAT FLOATER
ON YOUR KEY CHAIN.

13:36.875 --> 13:38.542
I GOT TO GET ONE OF THOSE.

13:38.542 --> 13:40.959
LOST MY KEYS OVERBOARD
TWICE IN THE PAST YEAR.

13:40.959 --> 13:43.583
I DO A LITTLE FISHING.
I GOT A 32-FOOT CONCEPT.

13:43.583 --> 13:45.125
WHAT ABOUT YOU?

13:45.125 --> 13:47.375
I GOT A ROWBOAT
WITH A HOLE IN IT.

13:47.375 --> 13:48.917
[ LAUGHS ]

13:48.917 --> 13:53.083
A LO MAJOR LOS PESCADOS
TE ENCUENTRAN.

13:53.083 --> 13:56.458
I DON'T SPEAK SPANISH, SIR.

13:56.458 --> 14:00.208
SORRY.
I JUST ASSUMED YOU WERE CUBAN.

14:00.208 --> 14:02.834
AMERICAN, PAL,
JUST LIKE YOU.

14:06.625 --> 14:08.500
JUST LIKE ME.

14:26.375 --> 14:28.625
HE'S ON HEAVY SEDATIVES
AT THE MOMENT.

14:28.625 --> 14:29.959
I THINK HE DESERVES THEM.

14:31.375 --> 14:33.041
I'LL WAIT.

14:37.625 --> 14:39.000
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

14:49.458 --> 14:50.709
HEY.

14:54.792 --> 14:56.834
MR. TUCCI.

15:00.500 --> 15:01.834
TONY.

15:06.250 --> 15:08.834
I'M GONNA FIND
THIS COCKSUCKER.

15:12.917 --> 15:14.333
I SWEAR.

16:19.917 --> 16:23.667
I DON'T UNDERSTAND
AMERICA'S OBSESSION WITH CARS.

16:26.083 --> 16:28.417
I CAN JUST IMAGINE
SQUEEZING RITA AND THE KIDS

16:28.417 --> 16:30.875
INTO THAT THING
AND HITTING THE OPEN ROAD --

16:30.875 --> 16:32.834
CRAMPED QUARTERS,
PUBLIC BATHROOMS,

16:32.834 --> 16:37.959
HOURS OF NOTHING
BUT CONVERSATION.

16:37.959 --> 16:41.291
IT'S SOMEONE'S AMERICAN
DREAM -- MY NIGHTMARE.

17:08.667 --> 17:12.041
THIS MUST BE
WHERE CASTILLO LOCKS THEM UP.

17:12.041 --> 17:14.709
BUT IF HE'S KILLING THEM
WHEN THEY CAN'T PAY,

17:14.709 --> 17:16.208
HE'S NOT DOING IT HERE.

17:19.625 --> 17:21.750
SO WHERE ARE THEY?

17:21.750 --> 17:23.834
♪ TENGA TUS BESOS ♪

17:23.834 --> 17:27.333
♪ QUé TENGA TU PELO
Y TU FORMA DE BAILAR ♪

17:27.333 --> 17:29.166
♪ QUé TENGA TUS OJOS ♪

17:29.166 --> 17:31.083
♪ QUé TENGA TUS MANOS ♪

17:31.083 --> 17:34.500
♪ QUé TENGA TU CUERPO
Y TUS GANAS DE BAILAR ♪

17:34.500 --> 17:36.333
AAH!

17:36.333 --> 17:39.166
AAH! AAH!

17:41.041 --> 17:42.500
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

17:42.500 --> 17:43.750
DEXTER MORGAN.

17:43.750 --> 17:45.250
Gerard here.

17:45.250 --> 17:47.083
There's a floater
down in South Beach morgue.

17:47.083 --> 17:49.333
COULD BE A MATCH
FOR YOUR MAID'S FIANCé.

17:49.333 --> 17:52.250
SHE'S A  MAID.
SHE'S NOT MY --

17:52.250 --> 17:54.458
IS IT ALL RIGHT
IF I BRING HER DOWN?

17:54.458 --> 17:56.041
THE SOONER, THE BETTER.

17:56.041 --> 17:59.000
OKAY, THEN. THANKS.
HAVE A GOOD DAY.

17:59.000 --> 18:01.166
TONIGHT AT THE SALSA ROOM.

18:01.166 --> 18:03.834
YOU GOT TO HELP ME
CELEBRATE MY PAY-GRADE BUMP.

18:05.458 --> 18:06.834
WHOA.

18:06.834 --> 18:09.709
ACTUALLY, I HAVE A PERSONAL
PROJECT I'M WORKING ON TONIGHT.

18:09.709 --> 18:11.291
BLOW IT OFF.
I'M BUYING.

18:11.291 --> 18:14.083
ANGEL, DO YOU HAVE THAT LIST
OF PRIORITIZED WITNESSES?

18:14.083 --> 18:16.208
I CAN'T DEAL
WITH 800 ANONYMOUS TIPS.

18:16.208 --> 18:17.875
I'M WORKING ON IT.

18:17.875 --> 18:21.208
WELL, HOW ABOUT YOU STOP
TALKING AND EARN  YOUR BUMP?

18:22.375 --> 18:24.041
Sexy.

18:24.041 --> 18:26.208
DON'T LEAVE ME HANGING
TONIGHT, BRO.

18:26.208 --> 18:27.792
IT'S YOU AND ME.

18:27.792 --> 18:31.875
I WONDER WHAT I DID TO MAKE HIM
THINK WE'RE SO CLOSE.

18:31.875 --> 18:35.083
I WONDER IF IT'D WORK ON RITA.

18:39.417 --> 18:42.041
DEXTER MORGAN --
I CALLED EARLIER.

18:42.041 --> 18:45.333
OH, RIGHT, YEAH,
ABOUT THE FLOATER.

18:45.333 --> 18:46.583
YEAH.

18:46.583 --> 18:51.417
HEY, JERRY, CAN YOU TAKE
THESE GUYS AROUND BACK?

18:51.417 --> 18:53.250
SHOULD I?

18:53.250 --> 18:55.458
NAH,
I'LL GO WITH HER.

18:55.458 --> 18:57.792
SHE MIGHT NEED
A SHOULDER.

18:57.792 --> 18:59.709
SHE SENSES I'M NOT A SHOULDER.

18:59.709 --> 19:03.333
BAD SIGN -- SHE'S CATCHING ON.

19:04.667 --> 19:07.583
I DON'T KNOW WHAT KIND OF IDIOT
THINKS AN INNER TUBE

19:07.583 --> 19:11.166
IS GONNA GET HIM
OVER 90 MILES OF OPEN OCEAN.

19:11.166 --> 19:15.125
IF YOU ASK ME, MAN,
IT'S DARWIN'S THEORY AT WORK.

19:26.125 --> 19:29.125
THAT MUST BE
WHAT LOVE LOOKS LIKE.

19:35.000 --> 19:38.208
THE INABILITY TO FEEL
HAS ITS ADVANTAGES...

19:41.959 --> 19:44.166
...SOMETIMES.

19:49.750 --> 19:51.291
HEY, DEXTER.

19:51.291 --> 19:52.875
HEY, MINDY.

19:52.875 --> 19:54.125
DO YOU NEED ANY HELP?

19:54.125 --> 19:56.125
NO.

19:56.125 --> 19:59.000
SO, ARE YOU GONNA GO
TO THE SPRING FORMAL?

20:00.542 --> 20:03.125
WHY WOULD I WANT
TO DO THAT?

20:11.333 --> 20:14.875
SHE WANTED YOU TO ASK HER
TO THE DANCE, DEXTER.

20:14.875 --> 20:16.875
THAT'S NOT
WHAT SHE SAID.

20:16.875 --> 20:19.709
WELL, YOU HAVE TO LEARN
THEIR SIGNALS.

20:19.709 --> 20:22.458
YEAH, WELL, I DON'T REALLY
CARE ABOUT GIRLS.

20:22.458 --> 20:24.834
OH.

20:24.834 --> 20:28.000
I JUST LIKE BEING ALONE.

20:31.542 --> 20:34.208
BUT MOST
NORMAL PEOPLE DON'T,

20:34.208 --> 20:36.542
AND IT'S IMPORTANT
THAT YOU SEEM NORMAL.

20:36.542 --> 20:39.208
EVEN THOUGH I'M NOT.
BECAUSE  YOU'RE NOT.

20:45.375 --> 20:48.041
WE'LL START YOU OFF
WITH A TEMPORARY PREFAB

20:48.041 --> 20:50.333
AND THEN MAKE ADJUSTMENTS
AS WE GO.

20:50.333 --> 20:52.375
RUDY HERE'S GONNA PUT ME
BACK TOGETHER AGAIN,

20:52.375 --> 20:54.625
GOOD AS NEW.

20:56.166 --> 20:58.000
HALF THE BATTLE
IS ATTITUDE,

20:58.000 --> 20:59.875
AND YOU HAVE
A GREAT ONE.

20:59.875 --> 21:02.208
WELL, I'M ALIVE.

21:02.208 --> 21:05.625
I DIDN'T SEE THAT HAPPENING,
BUT HERE I AM.

21:09.875 --> 21:13.417
YO, PRETTY BOY,
YOU'RE STEALING MY THUNDER,

21:13.417 --> 21:16.959
AND I GOT A HOTTIE
WAITING ON ME, SO...

21:16.959 --> 21:19.375
I DON'T KNOW.

21:19.375 --> 21:21.875
I JUST MIGHT HAVE TO
FIGHT YOU FOR THIS ONE.

21:23.000 --> 21:24.875
OKAY,
WE'LL ARM-WRESTLE LATER.

21:24.875 --> 21:26.417
NOW GET OUT OF HERE.

21:26.417 --> 21:29.834
WATCH OUT FOR THIS GUY.
HE'S A DOG.

21:29.834 --> 21:31.208
[ LAUGHS ]

21:31.208 --> 21:32.458
EXCUSE ME.

21:35.792 --> 21:38.917
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

21:38.917 --> 21:42.208
I KNOW WHAT YOU NEED, GUYS,

21:42.208 --> 21:44.291
BUT I DIDN'T SEE MUCH.

21:44.291 --> 21:47.083
WELL, ANY DETAIL WILL HELP,
MR. TUCCI.

21:47.083 --> 21:49.250
WELL...

21:49.250 --> 21:52.291
HE CAME UP ON ME
FROM BEHIND,

21:52.291 --> 21:55.792
AND HE WORE A MASK
WHEN HE MADE ME PUT THE...

21:55.792 --> 21:58.917
THE...

21:58.917 --> 22:01.250
THINGS ON THE ICE.

22:01.250 --> 22:02.750
OOPS.

22:02.750 --> 22:04.375
I'LL GET IT.

22:04.375 --> 22:06.750
ANGEL OF MERCY.
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:06.750 --> 22:08.583
JUST HOW MERCIFUL ARE YOU?

22:08.583 --> 22:10.166
OH, YOU ARE A DOG,
AREN'T YOU?

22:10.166 --> 22:12.208
SO THE LADIES TELL ME.

22:12.208 --> 22:14.250
CAN YOU TELL US
HOW TALL HE WAS

22:14.250 --> 22:16.000
OR IF HE WAS BLACK,
WHITE, LATINO?

22:16.000 --> 22:18.709
WHITE, I THINK.

22:18.709 --> 22:22.500
I'M GUESSING
MAYBE AVERAGE HEIGHT --

22:22.500 --> 22:27.458
NOT FAT, NOT THIN,
JUST AVERAGE.

22:27.458 --> 22:28.959
I DON'T KNOW.

22:30.542 --> 22:33.458
AND WHEN HE STARTED, YOU KNOW,
WORKING ON ME,

22:33.458 --> 22:36.542
I WAS BLINDFOLDED, SO...

22:36.542 --> 22:38.125
DID YOU HEAR ANYTHING?

22:38.125 --> 22:40.458
DID HE HAVE AN ACCENT
OR ANYTHING?

22:40.458 --> 22:44.291
HE DIDN'T TALK MUCH,
OR HE'D WHISPER.

22:44.291 --> 22:47.250
AND THAT'S ALL
YOU HEARD?

22:47.250 --> 22:49.750
EXCEPT THE RATS.

22:49.750 --> 22:53.250
SOMETIMES THEY WOULD
CRAWL UP ON THE BED,

22:53.250 --> 22:56.333
AND I'D HAVE TO SHAKE THEM OFF.

22:59.542 --> 23:01.667
SOME CRAP-ASS WITNESS
I AM, HUH?

23:01.667 --> 23:04.083
YOU'RE DOING FINE.
YOU'VE GIVEN US A LOT.

23:04.083 --> 23:06.375
YEAH?
YEAH.

23:08.500 --> 23:10.875
YOU KNOW, SOMETIMES WHEN I'M
TRYING TO REMEMBER SOMETHING,

23:10.875 --> 23:12.792
I CLOSE MY EYES.

23:12.792 --> 23:15.166
REALLY?
MM-HMM.

23:15.166 --> 23:17.500
WE COULD EVEN
BLINDFOLD YOU AGAIN.

23:21.667 --> 23:22.709
UM...

23:28.166 --> 23:29.875
...I'M KIND OF TIRED
RIGHT NOW.

23:29.875 --> 23:32.625
IT'S OKAY.
GET SOME REST.

23:32.625 --> 23:35.000
OFFICER MORGAN AND I
ARE LEAVING.

23:43.208 --> 23:45.166
ALONE.

23:45.166 --> 23:48.709
NO PRETENDING.
NO HIDING.

23:48.709 --> 23:50.542
[ FOGHORN BLOWS ]

24:05.125 --> 24:07.166
NO TIME TO RELAX.

24:07.166 --> 24:08.583
I'M TOO CLOSE.

24:08.583 --> 24:11.709
JORGE CASTILLO IS BAD.
THAT I KNOW.

24:11.709 --> 24:15.083
BUT BAD ENOUGH TO HAVE KILLED
YELINA'S FIANCé?

24:15.083 --> 24:18.583
THAT I HAVE TO PROVE.

24:18.583 --> 24:20.500
JORGE'S NOT-SO-HUMBLE ABODE.

24:20.500 --> 24:22.500
[ HORN HONKS ]
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

24:22.500 --> 24:24.291
YEESH -- NEW MONEY.

24:26.291 --> 24:28.417
NORMAL PEOPLE DREAM OF THIS --

24:28.417 --> 24:30.083
A NEW CAR, A BIG HOME,

24:30.083 --> 24:32.250
A BOAT
AT THE REEF SHORE MARINA...

24:35.750 --> 24:37.583
...AND A BEAUTIFUL WIFE.

24:37.583 --> 24:40.583
TOO BAD -- I NEVER ENJOY
MAKING SOMEONE A WIDOW.

24:40.583 --> 24:43.250
THEY'RE SO HAPPY.

24:43.250 --> 24:45.625
SHE HAS NO CLUE
WHO SHE'S WITH.

24:45.625 --> 24:50.417
MAYBE THAT'S THE SECRET
TO A SUCCESSFUL RELATIONSHIP.

24:52.417 --> 24:55.125
Doakes: MR. PERRY,
YOU WERE ON THE GROUNDS

24:55.125 --> 24:57.709
OF THE SAME HOSPITAL
WHERE WE FOUND MR. TUCCI.

24:57.709 --> 24:59.875
AND YOU WERE ALONE
THAT NIGHT?

24:59.875 --> 25:02.959
UH, IT WAS JUST ME
AND CAESAR, MY DOG.

25:02.959 --> 25:04.959
HE LIKES
ABANDONED BUILDINGS.

25:04.959 --> 25:06.291
CAESAR'S A RATTER.

25:06.291 --> 25:07.375
WHAT DID THIS GUY DO?

25:07.375 --> 25:09.458
WHY?
DOES HE LOOK FAMILIAR?

25:09.458 --> 25:11.542
YES, HE LOOKS LIKE

25:11.542 --> 25:14.041
AN ACTOR FROM THAT
JOHN SINGLETON MOVIE.

25:14.041 --> 25:15.667
WHAT WAS THAT?

25:15.667 --> 25:17.542
HOW ABOUT YOU FOCUS ON
WHETHER OR NOT HE WAS THE MAN

25:17.542 --> 25:19.333
YOU SAW AT THE OLD HOSPITAL
THAT NIGHT, MR. PERRY?

25:19.333 --> 25:21.208
WELL, IT WAS DIFFICULT
TO TELL.

25:21.208 --> 25:22.625
IT WAS DARK.

25:22.625 --> 25:24.291
YOU SAID
YOU GOT A LOOK AT HIM.

25:29.917 --> 25:31.291
HE HAD A CAP.

25:33.625 --> 25:36.959
HEY, IS THAT KG-230 HOOKED
INTO A DIGITAL CCTB NETWORK?

25:36.959 --> 25:39.792
OOH, YOU BETTER HAVE
A HELL OF A FIREWALL.

25:39.792 --> 25:42.000
YOU GET BETTER RESOLUTION
WITH THE 440.

25:42.000 --> 25:43.583
HELLO.

25:43.583 --> 25:45.417
WE'RE DONE HERE.

25:54.166 --> 25:57.500
GIVE ME A MINUTE.

25:57.500 --> 26:00.083
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

26:00.083 --> 26:02.250
[ SIGHS ]

26:02.250 --> 26:04.166
MORGAN, THANK MR. PERRY
FOR HIS HORSESHIT

26:04.166 --> 26:05.667
AND SEND HIM HOME.

26:05.667 --> 26:08.667
CHRIST ON A CRUTCH,
HE COULD TELL US SOMETHING.

26:08.667 --> 26:10.917
SERGEANT DOAKES
SAYS HE IS A LOOKY-LOO.

26:10.917 --> 26:12.875
WE GET DOZENS LIKE THAT EVERY
TIME A STORY HITS THE NEWS.

26:12.875 --> 26:15.000
NOW DO ME A FAVOR --
GET HIM OUT OF MY PRECINCT.

26:15.000 --> 26:16.500
THANK YOU.

26:18.917 --> 26:21.250
YOU COULD TRY BEING
A LITTLE MORE OPTIMISTIC.

26:21.250 --> 26:23.166
I MEAN, IF TONY TUCCI
CAN BE OPTIMISTIC,

26:23.166 --> 26:24.834
I THINK WE CAN.

26:24.834 --> 26:26.875
YOU MIGHT GET MORE
OUT OF PEOPLE.

26:26.875 --> 26:29.750
HOW DO YOU KNOW PERRY
DOESN'T KNOW ANYTHING?

26:29.750 --> 26:33.291
BECAUSE I'VE BEEN DOING THIS
A LOT LONGER THAN YOU.

26:33.291 --> 26:34.583
OKAY.

26:34.583 --> 26:36.417
THIS CASE
IS GETTING COLDER

26:36.417 --> 26:38.625
EVERY MINUTE YOU WASTE
ON BULLSHIT LIKE PERRY.

26:38.625 --> 26:40.875
AND WANTING TO BLINDFOLD
A TRAUMA VICTIM?

26:40.875 --> 26:42.959
WHAT THE FUCK
WERE YOU THINKING?

26:42.959 --> 26:46.875
TUCCI'S CLOSED FOR BUSINESS NOW,
AND YOU SHUT HIM DOWN.

26:46.875 --> 26:49.542
I...

26:49.542 --> 26:51.750
I WAS TRYING
A NEW APPROACH.

26:51.750 --> 26:54.208
[ SIGHS ]

26:54.208 --> 26:56.625
MAYBE YOU SHOULD
JUST LEARN THE BASICS

26:56.625 --> 26:58.792
BEFORE YOU REINVENT
THE DAMN WHEEL.

27:04.375 --> 27:07.250
♪ MAMBO YE  ♪

27:07.250 --> 27:09.417
♪ MAMBO YE  ♪

27:09.417 --> 27:12.291
♪ MAMBO YE  ♪

27:12.291 --> 27:15.250
♪ MAMBO YE  ♪

27:15.250 --> 27:17.625
♪ MAMBO YE, MAMBO YE  ♪

27:17.625 --> 27:20.625
♪ MAMBO YO, MAMBO USTED  ♪

27:20.625 --> 27:23.208
COME ON.
HOW CAN YOU NOT DANCE TO THIS?

27:23.208 --> 27:24.750
IT'S A GIFT.

27:24.750 --> 27:26.542
WE JUST NEED SOME MORE
PATRóN, COMPADRE.

27:26.542 --> 27:29.458
ANOTHER ROUND!
NO MORE FOR ME.

27:29.458 --> 27:31.208
I GOT TO GET UP EARLY --
KILLERS TO CATCH.

27:31.208 --> 27:32.709
FORGET THAT.

27:32.709 --> 27:34.709
THE NIGHT'S JUST BEGINNING,
RIGHT, LADIES?

27:34.709 --> 27:36.000
Woman: YES!

27:36.000 --> 27:37.750
LADIES, EXCUSE US.
ANGEL, COME HERE.

27:37.750 --> 27:41.458
YOUR WIFE --
SHE'S PROBABLY WORRYING.

27:41.458 --> 27:43.583
I DON'T KNOW WHAT SHE'D THINK
OF YOUR NEW FRIEND.

27:43.583 --> 27:45.709
SHE DON'T MIND
WHO I FLIRT WITH

27:45.709 --> 27:47.375
AS LONG AS I BRING HOME
LA PASION.

27:47.375 --> 27:48.625
LA PASION?

27:48.625 --> 27:50.792
YEAH, IT KEEPS
THE RELATIONSHIP ALIVE.

27:52.166 --> 27:55.750
HEY, WHAT ABOUT,
UH, COMMUNICATION, TRUST?

27:55.750 --> 27:57.917
LA PASION.

27:57.917 --> 27:59.625
WAIT.

27:59.625 --> 28:02.667
WHAT IF SHE WANTS
SOMETHING MORE?

28:02.667 --> 28:05.959
THEN YOU RECIPROCATE --
YOU KNOW...

28:05.959 --> 28:08.625
NO, I MEANT WHAT IF SHE WANTS
SOMETHING MORE EMOTIONALLY?

28:08.625 --> 28:10.333
DON'T GO DOWN
THAT EMOTIONAL ROAD.

28:10.333 --> 28:12.041
JUST GO DOWN ON HER.

28:12.041 --> 28:13.959
IT'S EASIER,
AND SHE'LL BE DISTRACTED.

28:13.959 --> 28:16.375
COME ON.
LET'S DANCE, ANGEL.

28:20.792 --> 28:22.542
SO...

28:26.375 --> 28:29.166
WHAT DO YOU WANT
TO DO NOW?

28:29.166 --> 28:31.166
Harry:
DANCE WITH HER, DEXTER.

28:31.166 --> 28:32.834
BE POLITE.

28:32.834 --> 28:35.458
GET HER PUNCH.
OPEN THE DOOR FOR HER.

28:35.458 --> 28:37.667
AND IF YOU FIND YOURSELF
ALONE WITH HER

28:37.667 --> 28:39.000
AND THINGS GET ROMANTIC --

28:39.000 --> 28:40.834
DAD, I'VE KISSED
A GIRL BEFORE.

28:40.834 --> 28:42.500
YOU HAVE?
YEAH.

28:42.500 --> 28:44.000
AND?

28:44.000 --> 28:46.333
I DON'T KNOW.
IT WAS OKAY.

28:48.166 --> 28:50.458
DEXTER, WOMEN
ARE DIFFERENT FROM MEN.

28:50.458 --> 28:52.083
WE'VE HAD THIS TALK, DAD.

28:52.083 --> 28:54.583
I'M SAYING THEY HAVE A WHOLE
DIFFERENT EXPERIENCE OF THINGS.

28:54.583 --> 28:56.417
WHEN THEY'RE WITH SOMEONE,
PHYSICALLY,

28:56.417 --> 28:57.792
THEY FEEL CONNECTED.

28:57.792 --> 28:59.750
AND THEY KNOW
WHEN YOU'RE NOT.

28:59.750 --> 29:02.208
THEY CAN SENSE IT
BECAUSE YOU'RE VERY EXPOSED.

29:02.208 --> 29:03.458
YEAH, YOU'RE NAKED.

29:03.458 --> 29:05.583
I MEAN EMOTIONALLY.

29:05.583 --> 29:08.166
SON, THIS IS GOING TO BE
VERY DANGEROUS FOR YOU.

29:08.166 --> 29:09.500
I CAN FAKE IT.

29:09.500 --> 29:13.375
BUDDY, YOU CAN LEARN
TO FAKE A LOT OF THINGS.

29:13.375 --> 29:16.041
THIS IS A TOUGH ONE.

29:32.750 --> 29:34.625
IS THIS IT?

29:39.875 --> 29:42.458
ANGEL, I'VE ONLY BEEN HERE
ONE TIME.

29:42.458 --> 29:44.291
I DON'T REMEMBER.

29:44.291 --> 29:46.458
WAKE UP.

29:51.709 --> 29:53.417
[ SIGHS ]

29:53.417 --> 29:55.792
YOUR WIFE'S
GONNA LOVE ME.

29:59.500 --> 30:01.375
THE PROBLEM WITH ACTING NORMAL

30:01.375 --> 30:04.417
IS NORMAL PEOPLE GET INTO
STUPID SITUATIONS LIKE THIS.

30:06.500 --> 30:09.125
OH. YOU SCARED
THE HELL OUT OF ME.

30:09.125 --> 30:10.166
SORRY, NINA.

30:10.166 --> 30:11.792
I'M DEXTER.
YOU REMEMBER?

30:11.792 --> 30:13.834
I WORK WITH ANGEL
DOWN AT THE STATION.

30:13.834 --> 30:15.208
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

30:15.208 --> 30:17.166
[ LAUGHS ]
IT'S FUNNY.

30:17.166 --> 30:19.792
WE WERE OUT CELEBRATING
ANGEL'S PAY-GRADE BUMP.

30:19.792 --> 30:22.083
HE GOT A RAISE?

30:22.083 --> 30:23.875
YEAH.

30:23.875 --> 30:27.291
WELL, AS YOU CAN SEE,

30:27.291 --> 30:30.583
HE, UH, HAD A LITTLE
TOO MUCH TO DRINK,

30:30.583 --> 30:32.625
SO I GAVE HIM A RIDE HOME.

30:32.625 --> 30:35.000
HE DOESN'T
LIVE HERE ANYMORE.

30:35.000 --> 30:37.041
OH.

30:40.500 --> 30:41.959
WE'RE SEPARATED.

30:41.959 --> 30:44.417
OH.

30:44.417 --> 30:47.875
SO...GOOD NIGHT.

30:47.875 --> 30:50.667
OH, OKAY.

30:52.417 --> 30:53.959
GOOD NIGHT.

30:55.875 --> 30:57.458
COME ON.

30:57.458 --> 31:00.333
LA PASION.

31:02.250 --> 31:05.166
ANGEL.

31:05.166 --> 31:08.709
ANGEL, WE'RE REALLY LATE
FOR WORK, AMIGO.

31:12.000 --> 31:13.583
[ GROANS ]

31:13.583 --> 31:15.750
I GUESS I HAD
ONE TOO MANY, HUH?

31:15.750 --> 31:17.875
AND THEN ABOUT 10 MORE.

31:27.166 --> 31:28.959
HOW DID I END UP HERE?

31:28.959 --> 31:31.583
YOU DON'T REMEMBER?

31:33.000 --> 31:34.834
SO YOU LIVE HERE, HUH?

31:34.834 --> 31:36.500
I LIVE HERE.

31:40.000 --> 31:42.250
YOU'RE KIND OF NEAT,
AREN'T YOU?

31:42.250 --> 31:45.667
BAD HABIT
INSTILLED BY MOM.

31:49.834 --> 31:52.333
[ AIR CONDITIONER WHIRRING ]

31:52.333 --> 31:53.583
OH.

31:55.959 --> 31:58.000
AAH.

32:05.500 --> 32:06.709
HEY.

32:09.125 --> 32:10.709
WE BETTER GET GOING.

32:10.709 --> 32:13.583
PRESSURE'S ON WITH THIS
ICE-TRUCK-KILLER SITUATION.

32:13.583 --> 32:15.458
YEAH. YOU GO AHEAD.
I'LL LOCK UP.

32:15.458 --> 32:17.583
I HAVE TO STOP
BY HOME ANYWAY.

32:17.583 --> 32:19.417
MY WIFE'S GONNA BE WORRIED.

32:19.417 --> 32:21.208
SHE GETS SO HOT
AND BOTHERED.

32:21.208 --> 32:24.542
NO, I'LL JUST WAIT,
AND I'LL DROP YOU AT YOUR CAR.

32:24.542 --> 32:26.792
WHERE'S YOUR BATHROOM?

32:30.041 --> 32:32.041
SOMEHOW IT'S REASSURING

32:32.041 --> 32:36.083
TO KNOW I'M NOT THE ONLY ONE
PRETENDING TO BE NORMAL.

32:36.083 --> 32:39.417
I FOUND HAIR ON THIS ONE THAT
DOESN'T BELONG TO TUCCI --

32:39.417 --> 32:40.917
RAT HAIR.

32:40.917 --> 32:43.375
I PROBABLY PICKED UP
A PARASITE JUST --

32:43.375 --> 32:44.917
DON'T TEST ME, MASUKA.

32:44.917 --> 32:46.875
UH, YOU SEE ALL THAT SHREDDING?

32:46.875 --> 32:49.250
HALF OF THIS SHEET
MUST BE LINING THEIR NESTS.

32:49.250 --> 32:51.542
THEY TOOK EVIDENCE
AWAY FROM THE CRIME SCENE?

32:51.542 --> 32:53.250
EXACTLY.
SO WE CHECK THEIR NEST.

32:53.250 --> 32:56.917
UH...WILD GOOSE CHASE,

32:56.917 --> 32:59.291
WITHOUT KNOWING
WHAT WE'RE LOOKING FOR.

32:59.291 --> 33:01.291
WE COULD TALK
TO TUCCI AGAIN.

33:01.291 --> 33:02.959
HE KNOWS
MORE THAN HE THINKS,

33:02.959 --> 33:04.917
AND MY GUT TELLS ME
HE CAN TAKE IT.

33:04.917 --> 33:07.417
'CAUSE YOU GOT THE INSTINCTS
OF A VETERAN ON THE FORCE.

33:07.417 --> 33:08.875
MASUKA, RUN THE SHEET.

33:08.875 --> 33:10.917
SEE IF WE CAN TRACE IT
TO MANUFACTURER.

33:10.917 --> 33:13.083
I'VE GOT COURT IN THE MORNING,
SO CALL ME ON MY CELL --

33:13.083 --> 33:15.208
ALL RIGHT, I GET IT.
I'M A NEWBIE.

33:15.208 --> 33:17.750
BUT YOU ARE OLD AND TIRED,
AND YOU NEED NEW EYES ON THIS.

33:17.750 --> 33:20.417
SO WHEN YOU'RE READY TO LET ME
DO MY JOB, YOU LET ME KNOW.

33:20.417 --> 33:23.542
AND DON'T YOU FUCKING
SAY A WORD, MASUKA.

33:23.542 --> 33:27.000
[ SIGHS ]

33:27.000 --> 33:30.458
HOW DO YOU GET RID OF THE ONES
WHO DON'T PAY OUT?

33:30.458 --> 33:33.667
DO YOU DROP THEM
IN THE MIDDLE OF THE OCEAN,

33:33.667 --> 33:35.375
TELL THEM TO SWIM FOR SHORE?

33:35.375 --> 33:36.917
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

33:36.917 --> 33:39.792
YOU CAN'T HIDE FOR LONG, JORGE.

33:39.792 --> 33:41.125
HELLO?

33:41.125 --> 33:42.917
Rita: Dexter, it's me.

33:42.917 --> 33:46.500
LOOK, I'M SORRY I HAVEN'T TALKED
TO YOU SINCE THAT PLACE.

33:46.500 --> 33:48.250
THE MORGUE.

33:48.250 --> 33:50.959
DO YOU THINK THEY'LL BE ABLE
TO CATCH WHOEVER DID THIS?

33:50.959 --> 33:54.458
I'M SURE
HE'LL GET WHAT HE DESERVES.

33:54.458 --> 33:56.291
How are you doing?

33:56.291 --> 33:58.041
STILL A LITTLE SHAKY.

33:58.041 --> 34:00.458
I HAVE SOME LATE-NIGHT WORK
I HAVE TO DO,

34:00.458 --> 34:04.166
BUT I COULD STOP BY EARLIER,
IF YOU WANT.

34:04.166 --> 34:06.291
MAYBE WE COULD
RENT A MOVIE.

34:06.291 --> 34:08.333
YEAH, I'LL PICK UP A DVD --

34:08.333 --> 34:11.041
SOMETHING LIGHT.

34:11.041 --> 34:13.917
[ RITA CRYING ]

34:25.750 --> 34:29.041
MAYBE IF I DON'T BLINK,
MY EYES WILL TEAR UP.

34:29.041 --> 34:32.166
[ SNIFFLING ]

34:32.166 --> 34:35.166
I HATE THIS.
I'M QUESTIONING EVERY MOVE.

34:35.166 --> 34:37.000
IT'S EXHAUSTING.

34:37.000 --> 34:39.750
I SHOULD JUST
BREAK IT OFF ALREADY,

34:39.750 --> 34:41.834
UNLESS I CAN PACIFY HER,

34:41.834 --> 34:46.125
GIVE HER...SOMETHING,

34:46.125 --> 34:48.542
RECIPROCATE.

34:48.542 --> 34:50.417
LA PASION.

34:54.625 --> 34:56.208
WHOA, UH, DEXTER?

34:59.458 --> 35:02.250
I'M SORRY.
I-I, UH...

35:02.250 --> 35:04.667
OH, I WAS JUST...

35:04.667 --> 35:07.959
YOU WERE SO GENEROUS
WITH ME.

35:07.959 --> 35:10.875
I WAS GONNA
RETURN THE FAVOR.

35:10.875 --> 35:13.542
OH, NO, THAT'S VERY SWEET,

35:13.542 --> 35:15.375
BUT I'M SORRY.

35:15.375 --> 35:18.083
I'M JUST NOT
IN THE MOOD FOR THAT.

35:19.667 --> 35:21.709
OH.

35:29.250 --> 35:31.000
Harry: THAT YOU, DEX?

35:31.000 --> 35:34.375
YEAH.
SORRY I'M LATE.

35:34.375 --> 35:37.291
IT'S OKAY, SON.
YOU MUST HAVE BEEN HAVING FUN.

35:37.291 --> 35:38.917
I PRETENDED TO.

35:38.917 --> 35:40.583
THAT'S GOOD, DEXTER.

35:40.583 --> 35:43.417
DAD?

35:43.417 --> 35:48.500
DO YOU THINK THAT MAYBE ONE DAY
I'LL FEEL IT FOR REAL?

35:49.917 --> 35:51.500
I HOPE SO, SON.

35:55.542 --> 35:57.750
I REALLY DO.

36:02.000 --> 36:05.083
ALONE, I'D BE BETTER OFF.

36:05.083 --> 36:07.750
RELATIONSHIPS
ARE TOO CONFUSING.

36:10.458 --> 36:12.625
BUT THIS I CAN FIGURE OUT.

36:12.625 --> 36:14.208
THIS I DO WELL.

36:14.208 --> 36:16.333
JORGE CASTILLO'S BOAT.

36:16.333 --> 36:18.792
IF HE'S A KILLER,
THEN THERE'S PROOF.

36:18.792 --> 36:21.875
THERE'S ALWAYS PROOF,
AND I'LL FIND IT.

36:38.583 --> 36:40.917
HAPPY, IN LOVE...

36:40.917 --> 36:42.667
THE PERFECT COUPLE.

36:42.667 --> 36:46.625
I WONDER IF RITA AND THE KIDS
WOULD LIKE FISHING.

36:46.625 --> 36:48.542
FOCUS.

37:00.792 --> 37:02.333
IF ONE OF THESE

37:02.333 --> 37:04.917
MATCHES THE CONTACT NUMBER
FOR ERNESTO'S COYOTE,

37:04.917 --> 37:07.333
YOU'RE IT, JORGE.

37:49.625 --> 37:52.834
HE DROWNS THEM HERE,
THEN DUMPS THEM OUT THERE.

37:52.834 --> 37:54.417
IF THEY WASH UP,

37:54.417 --> 37:57.083
IT'LL BE CHALKED UP
TO ANOTHER INNER-TUBE MISHAP.

38:51.542 --> 38:53.291
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

38:58.125 --> 39:01.542
YEP -- THIS I DO WELL.

39:03.709 --> 39:07.125
THINK ABOUT HIS SHOES.

39:07.125 --> 39:09.333
DID HE WALK WITH A LIMP?

39:11.083 --> 39:13.625
DID HE MOVE SMOOTHLY,
LIKE AN ATHLETE?

39:13.625 --> 39:17.500
TRY TO REMEMBER, TONY,
FOR ME.

39:17.500 --> 39:20.959
[ CHUCKLES ]
I WOULD IF I COULD, HON.

39:20.959 --> 39:23.333
YOU'RE A SWEET LADY,

39:23.333 --> 39:27.083
AND SMART --
USING YOUR CHARMS ON ME.

39:27.083 --> 39:29.041
NO, NO, I DON'T MIND.

39:29.041 --> 39:31.875
IT'S PROBABLY THE LAST TIME
A WOMAN WILL FLIRT WITH ME,

39:31.875 --> 39:33.709
LOOKING LIKE THIS.

39:33.709 --> 39:36.166
IT'S OKAY, TONY.

39:36.166 --> 39:37.792
MAYBE LATER.

39:37.792 --> 39:40.208
WE SHOULD TRY THE BLINDFOLD.

39:40.208 --> 39:42.125
WHAT?

39:42.125 --> 39:44.875
I DON'T WANT
TO DO THAT.

39:44.875 --> 39:46.667
I'M SORRY, MR. TUCCI.

39:46.667 --> 39:48.458
I CAN'T EVEN BEGIN TO IMAGINE
WHAT YOU'VE BEEN THROUGH,

39:48.458 --> 39:50.250
BUT IT'S OUR JOB
TO MAKE SURE

39:50.250 --> 39:52.500
THAT NOBODY ELSE
GOES THROUGH IT, TOO.

39:52.500 --> 39:56.083
SO, MORGAN, YOU'RE UP.

40:16.959 --> 40:20.000
HE WAS HARD TO HEAR.

40:20.000 --> 40:21.917
I NEVER KNEW WHERE HE WAS.

40:21.917 --> 40:23.959
SO HE'S AGILE.
THAT'S GOOD, TONY.

40:23.959 --> 40:25.417
WHAT ELSE DID YOU HEAR?

40:25.417 --> 40:28.875
RATS.

40:28.875 --> 40:30.542
ALWAYS THOSE DAMN RATS.

40:30.542 --> 40:33.458
TRY TO FOCUS ON HIM,  TONY.

40:33.458 --> 40:36.625
WHAT DID YOU HEAR?
WHAT DID YOU SMELL?

40:38.667 --> 40:39.959
MENTHOL.

40:39.959 --> 40:41.709
MENTHOL?

40:41.709 --> 40:44.750
YEAH, LIKE COUGH DROPS.

40:44.750 --> 40:47.917
HE CLEARED HIS THROAT A LOT.
YOU KNOW, LIKE --

40:47.917 --> 40:51.041
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

40:51.041 --> 40:55.041
HE UNWRAPPED THEM.

40:55.041 --> 40:57.166
I COULD HEAR THOSE WRAPPERS,

40:57.166 --> 40:59.125
THAT CRINKLY SOUND.

41:01.125 --> 41:03.166
AND HE SUCKED ON THEM.

41:05.625 --> 41:10.458
I COULD HEAR THEM CLICKING
AGAINST HIS TEETH WHEN HE...

41:10.458 --> 41:11.834
[ SNIFFLES ]

41:17.166 --> 41:21.041
THE SON OF A BITCH
LOVED THOSE FUCKING LOZENGES.

41:21.041 --> 41:22.417
[ SNIFFLES ]

41:26.917 --> 41:28.834
[ RATS CHATTERING ]

41:32.208 --> 41:33.834
NOTHING IN THIS NEST.

41:33.834 --> 41:36.583
WELL, CHECK ANOTHER FLOOR.
THEY'RE ALL OVER THIS DUMP.

41:38.041 --> 41:39.333
FUCK THIS.

41:41.166 --> 41:43.041
OH, SH--
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

41:43.041 --> 41:45.083
MASUKA.

41:45.083 --> 41:48.083
WE GOT ANOTHER ONE
OVER HERE.

41:48.083 --> 41:49.709
AHA. PROMISING.

41:49.709 --> 41:52.625
SEVERAL FRAGMENTS
FROM THE SHEET HERE.

41:52.625 --> 41:55.291
THESE RAT BASTARDS
WERE REPEAT CUSTOMERS.

41:57.792 --> 41:59.625
WHO HAD GARLIC FOR LUNCH?

41:59.625 --> 42:02.125
I'M GONNA PUNCH YOU
IN THE NECK.

42:02.125 --> 42:04.208
ACTUALLY...

42:04.208 --> 42:07.000
I THINK YOU'RE GONNA FRENCH ME.

42:18.041 --> 42:21.417
Dexter: ...2934.

42:21.417 --> 42:23.625
I LIKE BEING RIGHT.

42:23.625 --> 42:27.250
I USUALLY AM,
ABOUT THESE THINGS.

42:31.250 --> 42:33.834
"BE PREPARED" -- MY MOTTO.

42:33.834 --> 42:36.667
THE BOY SCOUTS AND I
HAVE THAT IN COMMON.

42:36.667 --> 42:39.542
OF COURSE, THERE'S NO MERIT
BADGE FOR TONIGHT'S OUTING.

42:47.333 --> 42:49.542
[ AIR HISSES ]

43:00.208 --> 43:02.208
WHAT ARE WE
LOOKING AT?

43:02.208 --> 43:05.709
THEY FOUND THE ICE-TRUCK
KILLER'S LOZENGE WRAPPER,

43:05.709 --> 43:07.500
THANKS TO YOUR SISTER.

43:07.500 --> 43:09.208
LOZENGE WRAPPER?

43:09.208 --> 43:11.875
HEY, AFTER TWO MONTHS OF FINDING
FUCK ALL IN THIS CASE,

43:11.875 --> 43:14.208
A LOZENGE WRAPPER'S
THE DAMN HOLY GRAIL.

43:14.208 --> 43:17.333
MY FAVORITE SERIAL KILLER
IS A LOZENGE EATER.

43:17.333 --> 43:18.917
HOW HUMAN OF HIM.

43:23.375 --> 43:24.834
WE HAVE A PARTIAL.

43:24.834 --> 43:28.291
[ GASPS ] PARTIAL PRINT --
A PARTIAL FUCKING PRINT!

43:28.291 --> 43:30.458
PROUD OF YOU, SIS.

43:30.458 --> 43:33.542
HEY, IT'S A CELEBRATION HERE.
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

43:33.542 --> 43:35.125
CRIME SCENE.

43:35.125 --> 43:37.542
EXCUSE ME.

43:37.542 --> 43:39.709
WHAT'S, UH --
WHAT'S GOING ON?

43:39.709 --> 43:41.750
WE'VE GOT OUR FIRST PIECE
OF TANGIBLE EVIDENCE

43:41.750 --> 43:42.959
ON THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER.

43:42.959 --> 43:44.291
A PARTIAL FUCKING PRINT.

43:44.291 --> 43:45.875
YOU RUN IT
THROUGH AFIS YET?

43:45.875 --> 43:47.875
IT DOESN'T EVEN MATTER
IF WE GET A MATCH.

43:47.875 --> 43:50.458
HE GETS PULLED IN FOR SOMETHING,
ANYTHING, WE GOT HIM.

43:50.458 --> 43:52.917
WE GET IT PHOTOED
BEFORE WE SCAN IT.

43:52.917 --> 43:54.917
[ INDISTINCT TALKING ]

43:58.583 --> 44:01.000
...AND LET'S KEEP WORKING
THE OLD HOSPITAL SITE, PEOPLE.

44:01.000 --> 44:03.583
YOU NEVER KNOW.
WE MIGHT GET LUCKY AGAIN.

44:03.583 --> 44:06.000
IT WASN'T LUCK.
GOOD WORK, MORGAN.

44:21.208 --> 44:23.333
AFUERA, VA.

44:23.333 --> 44:25.500
MUEVANSE.  COME ON.

44:30.125 --> 44:32.125
COME ON!

44:32.125 --> 44:33.625
ENTRAR, ENTRAR.

45:58.917 --> 46:00.375
[ GASPS ]

46:00.375 --> 46:01.709
God bless America.

46:11.208 --> 46:12.709
HON?

46:14.625 --> 46:16.375
WHERE ARE YOU?

46:19.000 --> 46:20.250
HONEY?

46:30.750 --> 46:32.625
HONEY, YOU IN HERE?

46:42.041 --> 46:44.166
iDERRITO A MI FAMILIA!

46:44.166 --> 46:45.750
[ SCREAMING ]

46:45.750 --> 46:48.166
GET BACK IN THERE,
YOU CUBAN PIECE OF SHIT!

46:52.333 --> 46:55.208
FUCKING ANIMALS.

46:55.208 --> 46:57.583
INCREDIBLE.

46:57.583 --> 46:59.875
THEY'RE AN EVEN BETTER MATCH
THAN I THOUGHT --

46:59.875 --> 47:01.792
TRUE PARTNERSHIP.

47:11.458 --> 47:14.125
YOU KNOW,
I RARELY DEVIATE FROM A PLAN,

47:14.125 --> 47:17.417
BUT I JUST DIDN'T HAVE THE HEART
TO SPLIT UP SUCH A...

47:17.417 --> 47:18.792
[ GROANS ]

47:18.792 --> 47:20.166
...PERFECT COUPLE.

47:24.041 --> 47:26.208
YOU TWO...

47:26.208 --> 47:31.792
HAVE QUITE A LUCRATIVE
OPERATION GOING.

47:31.792 --> 47:34.542
YOU'RE A REALLY GOOD TEAM.

47:38.917 --> 47:41.208
IT'S CLEVER, TOO.

47:41.208 --> 47:46.458
NO ONE QUESTIONS
ANOTHER DROWNED CUBAN MAN

47:46.458 --> 47:49.333
OR WOMAN...

47:49.333 --> 47:50.792
OR CHILD.

47:52.125 --> 47:53.792
SO, WHICH ONE OF YOU
THOUGHT THIS UP?

47:53.792 --> 47:56.291
THEY GET FREEDOM.
WE FREE THEM.

47:56.291 --> 47:58.291
THEY THANK US,
FOR GOD'S SAKE.

47:58.291 --> 48:02.041
FOR DROWNING THEM AND DUMPING
THEIR BODIES IN THE OCEAN?

48:02.041 --> 48:03.417
PLEASE.

48:03.417 --> 48:06.083
WE CAN PAY YOU.
WE HAVE MONEY.

48:06.083 --> 48:09.000
THAT'S WHAT
IT'S ALL ABOUT, RIGHT?

48:09.000 --> 48:10.083
I LOVE YOU.

48:10.083 --> 48:11.625
I LOVE YOU SO MUCH.

48:11.625 --> 48:13.667
I LOVE YOU SO MUCH.

48:20.667 --> 48:22.834
I'M GONNA ASK YOU A QUESTION.

48:22.834 --> 48:24.750
I WANT YOU
TO ANSWER ME HONESTLY.

48:24.750 --> 48:27.166
NO MORE BULLSHIT.
DO YOU UNDERSTAND?

48:29.000 --> 48:31.458
HOW LONG
HAVE YOU BEEN MARRIED?

48:31.458 --> 48:33.667
12 YEARS.

48:33.667 --> 48:36.000
HOW DO YOU LOVE EACH OTHER?

48:38.166 --> 48:41.000
YOU'RE LIKE ME,
AND YOU MAKE IT WORK.

48:41.000 --> 48:42.417
HOW?

48:42.417 --> 48:43.875
WE WANT THE SAME LIFE.

48:43.875 --> 48:46.375
WE BOTH --
WE WANT THE SAME THING.

48:46.375 --> 48:47.959
SAME LIFE.

48:47.959 --> 48:50.083
YOU SHARE THE SAME DREAM.

48:50.083 --> 48:51.583
YES, EXACTLY, YES.

48:51.583 --> 48:53.709
YES, THAT'S IT.

48:53.709 --> 48:55.709
THAT'S, UH...

48:57.875 --> 49:00.000
...HELPFUL.

49:00.000 --> 49:01.750
THANK YOU.

49:01.750 --> 49:03.709
[ GROANING ]

49:03.709 --> 49:04.917
NO.

49:04.917 --> 49:06.875
[ SALSA MUSIC PLAYS ]

49:18.750 --> 49:20.834
♪ DICEN POR AHí  ♪

49:20.834 --> 49:23.667
♪ ASí ES QUE SE BATE EL COBRE  ♪

49:23.667 --> 49:26.291
♪ UGALU, COCOLO  ♪

49:26.291 --> 49:29.250
♪ ENCIENDE MI PIN SALVAJE  ♪

49:39.959 --> 49:41.959
♪ DICEN POR AHí  ♪

49:41.959 --> 49:45.083
♪ ASí ES QUE SE BATE EL COBRE  ♪

49:45.083 --> 49:47.375
♪ UGALU, COCOLO  ♪

49:47.375 --> 49:50.583
♪ ENCIENDE MI PIN SALVAJE  ♪

49:50.583 --> 49:53.291
♪ UGALU, EL SALVAJE  ♪

49:53.291 --> 49:55.750
♪ UGALU  ♪

49:55.750 --> 49:58.583
♪ UGALU, EL SALVAJE  ♪

49:58.583 --> 50:00.917
♪ UGALU,  OOH, AHH ♪

50:00.917 --> 50:03.709
♪ UGALU, EL SALVAJE  ♪

50:03.709 --> 50:05.500
♪ UGALU  ♪

50:05.500 --> 50:07.458
♪ BUENO  ♪

50:10.458 --> 50:12.000
♪ EL SALVAJE  ♪

50:49.500 --> 50:52.542
I LIKE DOING THINGS PROPERLY,

50:52.542 --> 50:54.208
BUT I'M OUT OF TIME,

50:54.208 --> 50:56.834
AND I STILL
HAVE TO DISPOSE OF THEM.

50:58.166 --> 51:00.667
VALERIE GOT SHORT SHRIFT.

51:02.333 --> 51:04.917
BUT ALL IN ALL,
IT WAS A VERY GOOD NIGHT.

51:58.417 --> 52:00.709
I LIKE THIS PLACE.

52:00.709 --> 52:03.583
A LOT OF MEMORIES
ARE BURIED DOWN THERE.

52:09.125 --> 52:12.750
DEVIATING FROM THE PLAN
MAY HAVE BEEN ILL-ADVISED.

52:26.834 --> 52:31.625
BUT SOMETIMES
YOU JUST HAVE TO TAKE A RISK.

52:43.250 --> 52:45.333
AFTER ALL...

52:47.500 --> 52:50.500
...ISN'T THAT WHAT
RELATIONSHIPS ARE ALL ABOUT?

53:10.542 --> 53:12.792
DO YOU HAVE A DREAM...

53:15.917 --> 53:18.959
...FOR YOUR LIFE...

53:18.959 --> 53:22.083
YOUR FUTURE, I GUESS?

53:22.083 --> 53:24.041
OF COURSE.

53:24.041 --> 53:26.208
DO YOU?

53:26.208 --> 53:29.625
IT MIGHT SOUND WEIRD.

53:33.125 --> 53:35.917
[ SIGHS ]

53:37.291 --> 53:39.875
I WANT TO SOMEDAY
BE CONTENT

53:39.875 --> 53:44.250
AND JUST FEEL...

53:44.250 --> 53:48.500
COMFORTABLE,
LIKE EVERYONE ELSE.

53:48.500 --> 53:50.125
I WANT...

53:50.125 --> 53:52.166
A NORMAL LIFE.

53:57.917 --> 53:59.917
YEAH, A NORMAL LIFE.

53:59.917 --> 54:03.166
THAT'S ALL I WANT.

54:03.166 --> 54:04.750
JUST THAT.

54:04.750 --> 54:07.792
NO FAME AND FORTUNE --

54:07.792 --> 54:09.667
EXCITEMENT AT EVERY TURN?

54:09.667 --> 54:11.333
[ LAUGHS ]

54:11.333 --> 54:14.583
NO, I'VE HAD ENOUGH
EXCITEMENT.

54:14.583 --> 54:16.375
THANK YOU.

54:16.375 --> 54:19.208
NOW...
I'LL TAKE BORING.

54:19.208 --> 54:21.333
AVERAGE.

54:21.333 --> 54:23.834
ORDINARY.

54:23.834 --> 54:26.375
[ CHUCKLES ]

54:26.375 --> 54:28.375
THAT'S WEIRD, HUH?

54:32.458 --> 54:34.792
YEAH.

54:34.792 --> 54:36.375
[ CHUCKLES ]

